  "title": "vue-instantsearch: Passing percentage units to the global abs() function is deprecated.",
  "body": "### 🐛 Current behavior\n\nnpm run prod generates:\r\ntransforming (327) node_modules\\vue-instantsearch\\vue3\\es\\src\\components\\Menu.vue_vue&type=script&lang.jsDeprecation Warning: Passing percentage units to the global abs() function is deprecated.\r\nIn the future, this will emit a CSS abs() function to be resolved by the browser.\r\nTo preserve current behavior: math.abs(100%)\r\nTo emit a CSS abs() now: abs(#{100%})\r\nMore info: https://sass-lang.com/d/abs-percent\r\n\n\n### 🔍 Steps to reproduce\n\nnpm run prod\n\n### Live reproduction\n\nhttps://not\n\n### 💭 Expected behavior\n\nNo warning\n\n### Package version\n\nvue-instantsearch 4.8.4\n\n### Operating system\n\n_No response_\n\n### Browser\n\n_No response_\n\n### Code of Conduct\n\n- [X] I agree to follow this project's Code of Conduct",
